{"tid":777638,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[厲害了！] 強國PC版《魔物獵人 世界》因政策問題搶先下架！","createTime":"2018-08-13T05:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T05:43:29.000Z","uid":20815,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c305f3658465520dd7b752e2b1ca9212a9d2e69","tid":777638,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99071763/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F99071763%2F&d=gRnHp2AfHxnihZFnxWWf%2BLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=bccf4083\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99071763/</a><br />\n<br />\n《魔物獵人 世界》PC版在中國獨占發行的簡體中文版平台「騰訊WeGame」今日在官網宣佈，從本日 8 時起遊戲下架，對玩家造成的損失他們也表示將盡可能降到最低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/3826722l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F3826722l.jpg&h=b4c9f28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從官方公告中指出，《魔物獵人 世界》PC簡體版《怪物獵人世界》上線合規合法，但部分遊戲內容未完全符合政策法規要求，因此相關政府部門接到大量舉報，遊戲的營運文件已被取消，今日決定將游戲下線並停止發售所有遊戲內容，購買者可無條件申請退款，但還在繼續玩的玩家則無法保障後續體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/4/003/826/3826724n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F4%2F003%2F826%2F3826724n.jpg&h=63553a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是因為修改器舉報嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/3826730l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F3826730l.jpg&h=75fdb137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還是瘴氣之谷的霾害踩線了呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/3826723l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F3826723l.jpg&h=a3b2e6cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總之，這下連絢輝龍都看不到了...<br />\n<br />\n　騰訊先前風光宣佈，WeGame 將代理《魔物獵人：世界》PC 版本，並藉由卡普空官方製作簡體中文版，並將為簡體版製作相關便利工具。上線後 Steam 版本與 Wegame 版本經由簡體版玩家回報，Steam 版還沒有 Wegame 版連線順利，因此不少玩家登入帳號留下負評，現在成為了褒貶不一的狀態。<br />\n<br />\nWegame 平台在完美世界與 Valve 上個月宣布啟動「Steam 中國」計畫後，外界認為 Wegame 與 Steam 將彼此成勁敵，但此次 WeGame 緊急下架《魔物獵人：世界》PC版，看來 WeGame 最大的敵人並非 Steam 平台，而是自己人。"},{"pid":"214bdac2b14bbad608f7e95e844946e869623b44","tid":777638,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"這就是中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69317ef618c6543d7c83ac7326ed4b6c781db57e","tid":777638,"uid":37933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"ps4獵人傳來賀電<br />\n恭嘉依家玩嘅pc巴打唔駛對住外掛大陸狗"},{"pid":"7da7a23aab38b669a16ccf6dffb0e57b9f7b8b86","tid":777638,"uid":152726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"打MH用外掛不如唔好打"},{"pid":"939169a71c93d4dbd9bb88b7d542f0d1339b3a75","tid":777638,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"聽講唔係因為外掛問題<br />\n係比另一個代理唔到既代理商瘋狂report去文化部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb960d81c7f88363dc28f704886bf201a661031","tid":777638,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69317ef618c6543d7c83ac7326ed4b6c781db57e","tid":777638,"uid":37933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"ps4獵人傳來賀電<br />\n恭嘉依家玩嘅pc巴打唔駛對住外掛大陸狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"想問下強國 有冇PS4版"},{"pid":"6c4858765660459034b6661f5fb64a34379e1ba0","tid":777638,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939169a71c93d4dbd9bb88b7d542f0d1339b3a75","tid":777638,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"聽講唔係因為外掛問題<br />\n係比另一個代理唔到既代理商瘋狂report去文化部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"睇左篇大陸文都係咁講，好似話係網易搞到咁，商業背後...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63f696a33bf9afe8a97b284e0633cd77005e36e","tid":777638,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":